You are trying to check two values at same time. Hope it works for you

```
form.addEventListener(&#39;submit&#39;, (e) =&gt;{
    e.preventDefault();
    let messages = []
    if (email.value === &#39;&#39; &amp;&amp; password.value === &#39;&#39; || email.value == null &amp;&amp; password.value == null){
