    }
})
```

Your if condition in the validation is not valid:
```
email.value &amp;&amp; password.value === &#39;&#39; || email.value &amp;&amp; password.value == null
```
You cannot check if two values are empty at the same time, and since the field is a text field they can never be null. You can do:
```
email.value === &#39;&#39; || password.value === &#39;&#39;
```
Or chain multiple ifs to have separate messages:

